                     = XQJL0521-O-SME-TE(WK-I)

      *@       기업형소호토탈익스포져
               COMPUTE XDJL4052-O-CORP-TYP-SOHO-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
                     = XQJL0521-O-CORP-TYP-SOHO-TE(WK-I)

      *@       소매형소호토탈익스포져
               COMPUTE XDJL4052-O-RTLSAL-TYP-SOHO-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
                     = XQJL0521-O-RTLSAL-TYP-SOHO-TE(WK-I)

      *@       기타토탈익스포져
               COMPUTE XDJL4052-O-ETC-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
                     = XQJL0521-O-ETC-TE(WK-I)

      *@       소계
               COMPUTE XDJL4052-O-SUBT(WK-CUR-CNT)
                     = XQJL0521-O-SUBT(WK-I)

      *@       비중＝소계／전체합계＊１００
               INITIALIZE WK-EXHS-RT
               IF XQJL0523-O-SUM > 0
                  COMPUTE WK-EXHS-RT
                        = XQJL0521-O-SUBT(WK-I) /
                          XQJL0523-O-SUM
                  COMPUTE XDJL4052-O-WGHTZ(WK-CUR-CNT)
                        = WK-EXHS-RT * 100
      *@       그렇지않은경우　０으로　산출
               ELSE
                  MOVE ZERO
                    TO XDJL4052-O-WGHTZ(WK-CUR-CNT)
               END-IF

