           IF DBSQL-SELECT-CNT > ZEROS
               ADD 1 TO WK-CUR-CNT
      *@      총건수
              MOVE WK-CUR-CNT
                TO XDJL4052-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1
      *@       '합계'
               MOVE '합계'
                 TO XDJL4052-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD(WK-CUR-CNT)
      *@       대기업토탈익스포져
              MOVE WK-CNGL-TE
                TO XDJL4052-O-CNGL-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
      *@       중소기업토탈익스포져
              MOVE WK-SME-TE
                TO XDJL4052-O-SME-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
