                TO XDJL4052-O-CORP-TYP-SOHO-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
      *@       소매형소호토탈익스포져
              MOVE WK-RTLSAL-TYP-SOHO-TE
                TO XDJL4052-O-RTLSAL-TYP-SOHO-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
      *@       기타토탈익스포져
              MOVE WK-ETC-TE
                TO XDJL4052-O-ETC-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
      *@       소계
              MOVE WK-SUBT
                TO XDJL4052-O-SUBT(WK-CUR-CNT)
