             TO XQJL0524-I-GROUP-CO-CD

      *@   기준년월일
           MOVE XDJL4052-I-BASE-YMD
             TO XQJL0524-I-BASE-YMD

191220*@   국내외구분코드
           MOVE XDJL4052-I-HMAB-DSTCD
             TO XQJL0524-I-HMAB-DSTCD

      *@3.2.3 SLQIO프로그램 호출
      *@처리내용:QJL0524프로그램을 호출한다
      *@관련테이블:THKJL0066 접근유형:READ
           #DYSQLA QJL0524 XQJL0524-CA

      *@3.2.4 호출결과확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
      *비중을위한전체합계금액추출（전체）
                    MOVE ZERO
                      TO XQJL0524-O-SUM
               WHEN OTHER
      *@원장조회에러인경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 SELECT 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다
                    #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3250-XQJL0524-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@   OPEN
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3260-XQJL0522-OPEN-RTN.

      *@   초기화
           INITIALIZE XQJL0522-IN

      *@   변수 MOVE
      *@  그룹회사구분코드
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO XQJL0522-I-GROUP-CO-CD

      *@   기준년월일
           MOVE XDJL4052-I-BASE-YMD
             TO XQJL0522-I-BASE-YMD

191220*@   국내외구분코드
           MOVE XDJL4052-I-HMAB-DSTCD
             TO XQJL0522-I-HMAB-DSTCD

      *@   SQLIO OPEN
           #DYSQLA QJL0522 OPEN XQJL0522-CA

      *@   결과확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
      *@원장오픈에러인경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 OPEN 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다.
                    #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3260-XQJL0522-OPEN-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *  FETCH
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3270-XQJL0522-FETCH-RTN.

      *@   SQLIO FETCH
           #DYSQLA QJL0522 FETCH XQJL0522-CA

           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
      *@            출력파라미터 조립
                    PERFORM S3271-OUTPUT-SET-RTN
                       THRU S3271-OUTPUT-SET-EXT
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
      *@            데이터존재여부표시
                    MOVE CO-CHA-N TO WK-BIT
               WHEN OTHER
      *@원장패치에러인경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 FETCH 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다.
                    #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3270-XQJL0522-FETCH-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ 출력파라미터 SET
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3271-OUTPUT-SET-RTN.

      *@   OUTPUT DATA PUT LOOP
           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1
                   UNTIL WK-I > DBSQL-SELECT-CNT

               ADD 1 TO WK-CUR-CNT

      *@       내부신용평가등급구분코드
               MOVE XQJL0522-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4052-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD(WK-CUR-CNT)

      *@       대기업토탈익스포져
               COMPUTE XDJL4052-O-CNGL-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
                     = XQJL0522-O-CNGL-TE(WK-I)

      *@       중소기업토탈익스포져
               COMPUTE XDJL4052-O-SME-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
                     = XQJL0522-O-SME-TE(WK-I)

      *@       기업형소호토탈익스포져
               COMPUTE XDJL4052-O-CORP-TYP-SOHO-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
                     = XQJL0522-O-CORP-TYP-SOHO-TE(WK-I)

      *@       소매형소호토탈익스포져
               COMPUTE XDJL4052-O-RTLSAL-TYP-SOHO-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
                     = XQJL0522-O-RTLSAL-TYP-SOHO-TE(WK-I)

      *@       기타토탈익스포져
               COMPUTE XDJL4052-O-ETC-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
                     = XQJL0522-O-ETC-TE(WK-I)

      *@       소계
               COMPUTE XDJL4052-O-SUBT(WK-CUR-CNT)
                     = XQJL0522-O-SUBT(WK-I)

      *@       비중＝소계／전체합계＊１００
               INITIALIZE WK-EXHS-RT
               IF XQJL0524-O-SUM > 0
                  COMPUTE WK-EXHS-RT
                        = XQJL0522-O-SUBT(WK-I) /
                          XQJL0524-O-SUM
                  COMPUTE XDJL4052-O-WGHTZ(WK-CUR-CNT)
                        = WK-EXHS-RT * 100
      *@       그렇지않은경우　０으로　산출
               ELSE
                  MOVE ZERO
                    TO XDJL4052-O-WGHTZ(WK-CUR-CNT)
               END-IF

      *@합계처리
      *@       대기업토탈익스포져
               ADD XDJL4052-O-CNGL-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
                TO WK-CNGL-TE

      *@       중소기업토탈익스포져
               ADD XDJL4052-O-SME-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
                TO WK-SME-TE

      *@       기업형소호토탈익스포져
               ADD XDJL4052-O-CORP-TYP-SOHO-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
                TO WK-CORP-TYP-SOHO-TE

      *@       소매형소호토탈익스포져
               ADD XDJL4052-O-RTLSAL-TYP-SOHO-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
                TO WK-RTLSAL-TYP-SOHO-TE

      *@       기타토탈익스포져
               ADD XDJL4052-O-ETC-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
                TO WK-ETC-TE

      *@       소계
               ADD XDJL4052-O-SUBT(WK-CUR-CNT)
                TO WK-SUBT

      *@       비중
               ADD XDJL4052-O-WGHTZ(WK-CUR-CNT)
                TO WK-WGHTZ

           END-PERFORM

      *@합계부출력
           IF DBSQL-SELECT-CNT > ZEROS
               ADD 1 TO WK-CUR-CNT
      *@      총건수
              MOVE WK-CUR-CNT
                TO XDJL4052-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1
      *@       '합계'
               MOVE '합계'
                 TO XDJL4052-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD(WK-CUR-CNT)
      *@       대기업토탈익스포져
              MOVE WK-CNGL-TE
                TO XDJL4052-O-CNGL-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
      *@       중소기업토탈익스포져
              MOVE WK-SME-TE
                TO XDJL4052-O-SME-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
      *@       기업형소호토탈익스포져
              MOVE WK-CORP-TYP-SOHO-TE
                TO XDJL4052-O-CORP-TYP-SOHO-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
      *@       소매형소호토탈익스포져
              MOVE WK-RTLSAL-TYP-SOHO-TE
                TO XDJL4052-O-RTLSAL-TYP-SOHO-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
      *@       기타토탈익스포져
              MOVE WK-ETC-TE
                TO XDJL4052-O-ETC-TE(WK-CUR-CNT)
      *@       소계
              MOVE WK-SUBT
                TO XDJL4052-O-SUBT(WK-CUR-CNT)
      *@       비중＝１００（신병기대리요청）
      *       MOVE WK-WGHTZ
      *         TO XDJL4052-O-WGHTZ(WK-CUR-CNT)
              MOVE CO-NUM-100
                TO XDJL4052-O-WGHTZ(WK-CUR-CNT)
           ELSE
      *@      총건수＝０
              MOVE ZERO
                TO XDJL4052-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1
           END-IF
           .
       S3271-OUTPUT-SET-EXT.
           EXIT.
